---
import Announcement from "./Announcement.astro";
---


<section id="home-announcements" class="container mb-4">
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4 justify-content-center">
        <Announcement
            title="Upcoming FTC Kickoff"
            image="/img/ftc/2022/speaker.webp"
            alt="Kyle Flynn, CTO of the Orange Alliance, presents his FIRST journey to FTC teams during kickoff in 2022"
            links={[
                {
                    text: "See event schedule and map",
                    link: "/events/ftc-kickoff",
                },
                {
                    text: "Sign up to volunteer",
                    link: "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1APPI9L76-n7B-cM7JXfZwbMEv8TdedkOScCtLDttj1Y/edit#gid=943429782",
                    tooltip: "umich.edu login required"
                },
            ]}
        >
            FAMNM will host a kickoff for the 2023&ndash;2024 FIRST Tech Challenge season, <i>CENTERSTAGE</i>, on
            <time datetime="2023-09-09">September 9th, 2023</time>. The registration period is over, but
            you may still sign up to volunteer in positions that don't interact with middle-school students.
        </Announcement>
        <Announcement
            title="Request mentoring from FAMNM"
            image="/img/teams/fr_mentor2.jpg"
            alt="Freelance mentors from FAMNM helping out an FRC team"
            links={[
                {
                    text: "Request mentoring",
                    link: "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdxwCNhkoOetBASDQuRNeuxTaVqER6vIT36LixpFXDfwyfEEA/viewform"
                }
            ]}
        >
            If you would like your team to receive mentoring from FAMNM students at any level of commitment (from one-time help to full time mentorship), please fill out the request form below!
        </Announcement>
        <Announcement
            title="Interested in joining FAMNM?"
            image="/img/index/announcements/game-night-2018.jpg"
            alt="FAMNM game night"
            links={[
                {
                    text: "Interest form",
                    link: "https://forms.gle/UVQ5rXoXxjexmo8e6",
                },
            ]}
        >
            Come to our Fall 2023 General Body Meetings on <b>Tuesdays at 7 PM</b> (check Slack for location), and
            fill out our <a href="https://forms.gle/UVQ5rXoXxjexmo8e6">Fall 2023 interest form</a>
            so that we can add you to our Slack workspace and mailing list.
        </Announcement>
    </div>
</section>
